<span id="freeTextContainer1062610393120955313">This book brought out so much potential but it turned out to be a really big mess.<br/>The ending especially left a bad taste. I did not like the cliche in the plot resolve.<br/>In truth I would have loved to read about the things being mentioned in the last chapter in more detail and again I am left agitated by the wrap up of the book..</span>

          </span>
