      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laura..devouring books like crumpets" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laura..devouring books like crumpets" href="/user/show/44244213-laura-devouring-books-like-crumpets">Laura..devouring books like crumpets</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44244213-laura-devouring-books-like-crumpets?shelf=over-reading-challenge-2019">over-reading-challenge-2019</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2521375164" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5048401314695312436">I can see how Anita Blake is changing turning more sexual but i still love it... occasionally its a bit too much and the customs and traditions of all the different paranormal beings is mind boggling (v similar to Merry Gentry) in that respect.... with so much sex the thrill and horror does get taken out a little... but i still love this series and cant wait for next book!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


